        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig. 28 shows the colocalization of MAP2 and actin on group of filaments (big arrow) associated with the PSD (small arrow). Both antigens also colocalized in PSD (arrowhead).\n\nFig. 1 shows the specificity of the MAP2-antibody.. Experimental description: \"Electron microscopy. 10 rats kept under standard laboratory\nconditions were anesthetized with urethane and perfused\ntranscardially (3 lb/in 2)...\" p. 448" ;
